)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div></div></nav><div class=\"mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] flex gap-5 flex-shrink-0\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/kvrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors\">Instagram</a></div></div><div class=\"fixed inset-0 z-[300] transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\" aria-label=\"Shopping bag\" class=\"fixed top-0 right-0 bottom-0 z-[400] w-full max-w-[400px] bg-[var(--color-bg)] flex flex-col transition-transform duration-[550ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)] translate-x-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\"><h2 class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.14em] uppercase\">Bag</h2><button aria-label=\"Close bag\" class=\"p-2 -mr-2 opacity-40 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3l12 12M15 3L3 15\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto scrollbar-thin\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full px-6 text-center gap-5\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Your bag is empty.</p><a href=\"/shop\"><button aria-busy=\"false\" class=\"relative inline-flex items-center justify-center font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-150 ease-out select-none whitespace-nowrap -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent bg-transparent text-kvrn-text border border-kvrn-text hover:bg-kvrn-text hover:text-kvrn-bg active:bg-[#333333] disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:pointer-events-none h-10 px-5 text-[11px]\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">Browse collection</span></button></a></div></div></div><main id=\"main-content\"><div class=\"pt-[56px]\"><div class=\"container-kvrn section-padding max-w-2xl\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-10\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-kvrn-muted tracking-wide\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li aria-hidden=\"true\">·</li><li class=\"text-kvrn-text\" aria-current=\"page\">Cookie Policy</li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"font-display font-light text-[40px] md:text-[48px] leading-none tracking-tighter mb-3\">Cookie Policy</h1><p class=\"label-11 text-kvrn-muted mb-14\">Last updated: 1 January 2025</p><div class=\"space-y-10 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><section><p>This policy explains what cookies are, what we use them for, and how to control them. Under PECR (Privacy and Electronic Communications Regulations), we need your consent before placing non-essential cookies on your device.</p></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-4\">Essential cookies</h2><p class=\"mb-4\">Required for the site to function. Cannot be opted out of.</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-[13px]\" aria-label=\"Essential cookies\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-kvrn-border\"><th class=\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\">Cookie</th><th class=\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\">Purpose</th><th class=\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\">Expires</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"divide-y divide-kvrn-border\"><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 font-mono text-[12px] text-kvrn-text\">kvrn_cart</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">Stores your shopping bag contents</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">30 days</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 font-mono text-[12px] text-kvrn-text\">kvrn_cookie_consent</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">Remembers your cookie preferences</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">1 year</td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-4\">Analytics cookies (optional)</h2><p class=\"mb-4\">Only set if you accept. Used to understand how visitors use our site.</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-[13px]\" aria-label=\"Analytics cookies\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-kvrn-border\"><th class=\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\">Cookie</th><th class=\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\">Provider</th><th class=\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\">Purpose</th><th class=\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\">Expires</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"divide-y divide-kvrn-border\"><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 font-mono text-[12px] text-kvrn-text\">_ga, _ga_*</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">Google Analytics 4</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">Distinguishes users and sessions</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">2 years</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 font-mono text-[12px] text-kvrn-text\">_clck, _clsk</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">Microsoft Clarity</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">Session recordings</td><td class=\"py-2.5\">1 year / 1 day</td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\">Advertising cookies</h2><p>We do not use advertising or tracking cookies. KVRN does not run paid advertising.</p></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-4\">Manage your preferences</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">You can change your analytics cookie preference at any time. Declining removes analytics cookies and prevents new ones being set.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><button class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest uppercase border border-kvrn-text px-4 h-9 hover:bg-kvrn-text hover:text-kvrn-bg transition-colors duration-150\">Accept analytics</button><button class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest uppercase text-kvrn-muted hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors duration-150\">Decline analytics</button></div><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">You can also control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling essential cookies will affect site functionality (shopping bag will not persist).</p></div></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><p>For more information, see our<!-- --> <a class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a>. Questions? Email<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@kvrn.com\" class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\">hello@kvrn.com</a>.</p></section></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg)]\" aria-label=\"Site footer\"><div class=\"kvrn-container\"><div class=\"py-16 md:py-24 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-10 md:gap-16\"><div class=\"col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><a class=\"block text-[14px] font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-5\" href=\"/\">KVRN</a><p class=\"text-[13px] text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-[200px]\">Designed slowly.<br/>Built to remain.</p><div class=\"flex gap-5 mt-6\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/kvrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-150\" aria-label=\"KVRN on Instagram\">Instagram</a></div></div><div><p class=\"kvrn-label mb-5\">Shop</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/shop\">All Products</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/products/kvrn-heavyweight-hoodie\">Heavyweight Hoodie</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] 